[font=Comic Sans MS]                      [size=3][color=#f9cb9c] Q)Why do you use both RaceMenu and ECE and for what do I need ece for?[/color][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]
[/url]                   A)Because ECE has some features that are better than the ones in racemenu in my                                                              opinion,like head mesh and character creation by itself is easier and better.But on the                                                    other hand there are Racemenu's overlays for tattoos and warpaints and easier                                                                character saving so why not combining?
[/size][/font]                             
               [font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]     [color=#f9cb9c]Q)Which enb do you use?[/color]
                    A) A mixture of rampage,snapdragon and somber's Jyggalag[/size][/font]
[font=Comic Sans MS][size=3] 
                    [color=#f9cb9c]Q)How do I fix neck color problem?[/color]
[/size][/font]                        [font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]A)Just type showracemenu go to body and change entire body color to 2 and you should                                                       be fine[/size][/font]
                         
                    [font=Comic Sans MS]   [size=3][color=#f9cb9c]Q)Why are these characters looking different in my game than yours?[/color]
